Sarah Vaughan had talent that is matched by few in jazz history.  This CD features arrangements that take full advantage of that talent.  In addition, Sarah Vaughan possesed a quality in her voice that makes it, although not the musicians behind that voice, sound as if these recordings could have been done last year.  She was truly one of the great female singers in not only jazz, but in American History. ~ A Customer, Amazon
